00:16:58.039 --> 00:17:06.039
And so a healthy fear of Jehovah means that we don't want to displease Him in any way.

00:17:06.039 --> 00:17:19.039
So a fear of Jehovah helps us so that as we're moving along, if anything comes our way, we're ready to stop if we shouldn't engage in that activity.

